{"tid":1406982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意撚收皮啦","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:35:03.000Z","uid":285367,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a92790b42410e2c5ec2b9962120258c9ad2c7a5","tid":1406982,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:32:41.000Z","msg":"到今日今日都仲唔知香港人最大特點係乜?<br />\n係隨機應變呀<br />\n隨機應變姐係咩<br />\n姐係習慣呀<br />\n鉛水可以慣 普教中可以慣<br />\n身邊普通話多過廣東話都可以慣<br />\n有咩唔可以慣呀<br />\n連Tear gas 開槍都慢慢慣緊<br />\n你睇下上環開36槍仲有幾多人講?<br />\n玩火點點點 整交通燈點點點 塞紅隧點點點<br />\n等多幾日啦 咪又係會慣<br />\n<br />\nbtw 認同某位連仔講做野要考慮市民感受<br />\n唔係講緊因為佢地而唔做某啲野<br />\n係起碼都要比返啲基本尊重人<br />\n我地係一條team 唔洗屌嚟屌去"},{"pid":"eec2d02edf44953d4b44f0ec827708e237710ffd","tid":1406982,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c1a74bd2f72e8571051257dfccab778d19468b9","tid":1406982,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">史上首次佔領路軌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n8月5日東鐵線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1407848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1407848</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8月5日全港被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90cdca989f664f3f39fa530e41961cf72427175f","tid":1406982,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c1a74bd2f72e8571051257dfccab778d19468b9","tid":1406982,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">史上首次佔領路軌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n8月5日東鐵線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1407848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1407848</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8月5日全港被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405650\" data-auto-lin